### {233}{}{Young people are impatient. Working on plantations is exhausting for them. But the earth gives its fruits only to those who have worked hard for many years. So is my Jacob. He went to the rangers, so as not to mess around in the beds. The first encounter with the raiders during the patrol took his life.}
{233}{}{年轻人不耐烦。在种植园工作对他们来说很累人。但是，地球只把它的果实送给那些辛勤工作多年的人。我的雅各布也是。他去找护林员，以免在床上乱来。巡逻时第一次遇到袭击者就夺去了他的生命。 -- Young people are impatient. Working on plantations is exhausting for them. But the earth gives its fruits only to those who have worked hard for many years. So is my Jacob. He went to the rangers, so as not to mess around in the beds. The first encounter with the raiders during the patrol took his life.}
