### {241}{}{Rangers bury their brothers according to the old tradition - they bury them in the ground. A cartridge is placed in the grave, usually a revolver caliber. If there is no revolver, any other one will do. And if there is no such thing, then they put a cartridge case or a fired bullet. By this they mean to say that even after death one should not lose the strength of the spirit.}
{241}{}{游骑兵按照古老的传统埋葬他们的兄弟――他们把他们埋在地里。坟墓里放着一个子弹，通常是左轮手枪口径。如果没有左轮手枪，其他人都可以。如果没有，他们就会放一个弹壳或一发子弹。他们的意思是说，即使死了，也不应该失去精神的力量。 -- Rangers bury their brothers according to the old tradition - they bury them in the ground. A cartridge is placed in the grave, usually a revolver caliber. If there is no revolver, any other one will do. And if there is no such thing, then they put a cartridge case or a fired bullet. By this they mean to say that even after death one should not lose the strength of the spirit.}
